function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

	local idPlayer = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()

	idRelic = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(ID_RELIC, ID_RELIC_GIZMO, false, 0, 0)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idRelic, ID_RELIC_GIZMO)
	Hydra.QActorAnim(idRelic, "AnimKey_Opening")
	Hydra.QActorDelete(idRelic)
	
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(S_CONVO_CONFUSION, idPlayer)

end

function Start()

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idGizmoLoc) then
		idBarbPot = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(S_STEP_BARB_POT, idGizmoLoc, false, 0, 0)
		Hydra.QActorKill(idBarbPot)
	else
		idBarbPot = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(S_STEP_BARB_POT, ID_MARKER_BURST_LOC, false, 0, 0)
		Hydra.QActorKill(idBarbPot)
	end
	
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectDuration(ID_MARKER_VFX_SOURCE, 0.5)	-- controls the travel time of each missile. Higher values means slower projectiles
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(ID_MARKER_VFX_SOURCE, 3)
	
	idAttractorVFX = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(ID_MARKER_VFX_SOURCE, ID_MARKER, S_ATTRACTOR_VFX, true)
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffect(ID_MARKER_VFX_SOURCE, idAttractorVFX)
	Hydra.EventSendToActor("Relic Appear", idSelf, idSelf)
	
end
